headline: Ulta Beauty Launches UB Marketplace, Expanding E-commerce With 100 New Brands
summary: The invite-only platform offers a selection across emerging categories, with plans to scale rapidly.

headline: Ulta Beauty’s marketplace launches
summary: UB Marketplace, which is open to brands by invitation only, is introducing over 100 new brands to start and will scale quickly over the next year or so.
